Package: covizr
Title: Easy access to Covid-19 data from Our World in Data and generates COVID-19 charts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rohit", "Rawat", email = "rrrohit28@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
