Description: covizr is a R package that provides easy access to Covid-19 data from Our World in Data, as well as functions to generate relevant Covid-19 charts and summaries easily. We aim to make covizpy simple and easy to use. Our goal is to enable anyone with basic Python programming knowledge to access and visualize Covid-19 data, and make their own informed decisions and conclusions.
